# Factorio Learning Environment

A Python framework for training and evaluating AI agents in the Factorio game environment.

## Installation

```bash
pip install factorio_learning_environment
```

## Usage

```python
from factorio_learning_environment.agents import BasicAgent
from factorio_learning_environment.eval import Evaluator

# Create an agent
agent = BasicAgent()

# Evaluate the agent
evaluator = Evaluator()
results = evaluator.evaluate(agent)
print(results)
```

## Documentation

For detailed documentation, visit the [GitHub repository](https://github.com/JackHopkins/PaperclipMaximiser).
